data.name: DeleteInterstateSupportOrder
data.value: delete from CKT_INTERST_SUP_OR where (CCA_TRANSACTION_DT = @ccaTransactionDt) and (SYS_GENERATED_ID = @sysGeneratedId) and (CCA_TRAN_SER_NUM = @ccaTranSerNum)

data.name: ReadInterstateCase
data.value: select top(1) TRANS_SERIAL_NBR, TRANSACTION_DATE from CKT_INTERST_CASE with(readuncommitted) where (TRANS_SERIAL_NBR = @transSerialNbr) and (TRANSACTION_DATE = @transactionDate)

data.name: ReadInterstateSupportOrder
data.value: select top(1) CCA_TRANSACTION_DT, SYS_GENERATED_ID, CCA_TRAN_SER_NUM from CKT_INTERST_SUP_OR where (SYS_GENERATED_ID = @sysGeneratedId) and (CCA_TRAN_SER_NUM = @ccaTranSerNum) and (CCA_TRANSACTION_DT = @ccaTransactionDt)
